    "updated_at": "2025-01-30T02:50:33Z",
    "body": "Hey @krxecs,\n\nJust a quick heads-up—the Gradle symbol was added to the nerd-font-symbols preset in [this commit](https://github.com/starship/starship/commit/6282209), which is included in Starship v1.22.1. Since you're currently using v1.20.1, updating should resolve the issue.\n\nHope that helps! 😊",
